    "body": "this error still in docs, see https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/configure/js/#connector-param-render-refine\r\n\r\nneed to import connectConfigure, this fix below worked for me\r\n\r\n`import { connectConfigure } from 'instantsearch.js/es/connectors';`\r\n\r\n`const customConfigure = connectConfigure(\r\n  renderConfigure,\r\n  () => {}\r\n);`",
